 -  - paper title: On the influence of the band structure of insulators and image forces on the spectral characteristics of metal-insulator film systems
 - abstract: The potential profiles, work functions, and Schottky barriers of aluminum films with the ideal vacuum/Al(111)/SiO3 and vacuum/Al(111)/Al2O3 interfaces and the SiO2/Al(111)/Al2O3 sandwich have been calculated self-consistently with the use of the Kohn-Sham method and the model proposed in our previous work taking into account image forces and the conduction band of the insulator.
